{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/dawn-theme-move-title-above-images-on-product-pages","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1515,"date":"2022-03-08T04:26:50","date_gmt":"2022-03-08T04:26:50","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1515"},"modified":"2022-03-08T04:28:40","modified_gmt":"2022-03-08T04:28:40","slug":"dawn-theme-move-title-above-images-on-product-pages","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/dawn-theme-move-title-above-images-on-product-pages/","title":{"rendered":"Dawn theme: move title above images on product pages"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Before presenting your product&#8217;s images, you may want to let your customer know what it actually is that they are looking at. On desktop, customers can read the title and look at the images at the same time, however, on most mobile devices, the title will be seen only after some scrolling is done.<br><br>If you&#8217;d like to move your product&#8217;s title above the images on mobile devices, you are at the right place: with just a bit of simple coding you can achieve that. Let&#8217;s begin!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-the-code-to-the-theme\">Adding the code to the theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Search for this file:<br><br>main-product.liquid<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"885\" height=\"541\" class=\"wp-image-1516\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-1.jpg 885w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-1-850x520.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-1-768x469.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 885px) 100vw, 885px\" /></li><li>Now, within the <strong>main-product.liquid</strong> file, press <em>CTRL + F</em> (or <em>command + F </em>on Mac) to open the search menu</li><li>Search for the following text: <strong>product__media-wrapper</strong></li><li>Copy the code below and paste it <strong>below</strong> the line you found.<br><br>[gist]b650c330058d69748eb2b8b354624601[gist]<br></li><li>It should look like this:<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1203\" height=\"810\" class=\"wp-image-1518\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-2.jpg 1203w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-2-850x572.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-2-1200x808.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-2-768x517.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1203px) 100vw, 1203px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-container-6248e72548085 wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-conclusion\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The way it works is essentially by duplicating the title and managing its visibility via CSS. It is also SEO friendly since this particular approach makes use of “display: none;”. Google crawlers ignore all elements that are set to “display: none;”, therefore it won&#8217;t consider that your product page has a duplicated title.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some other copy/paste tutorials you may be interested in:<br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Add a slideshow section to Dawn without any apps</a> <br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-add-a-read-more-button-to-the-product-page\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Add a &#8220;read more&#8221; button to Dawn&#8217;s product page</a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Improve your website&#8217;s safety: block right click, image copying and more</a></p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn the easiest and fastest way to move your Dawn theme&#8217;s mobile title without affecting the Desktop&#8217;s design.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1522,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,435,82],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-above-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-above-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/title-above-1200x675.png","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial","Dawn Theme","product page"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1515"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"